e work, adapt to changing workloads with excellent organizational skills Ability to work independently The Saskatchewan Health Authority offers competitive salaries and a comprehensive benefits package.Those who thrive working in a fast-paced, stimulating environment will be interested in joining our team.Interested applicants are invited to submit a cover letter, resume and three references in confidence, quoting Job Number RQ-28041, by June 14, 2024 to: Email: susan.baer@saskhealthauthority.caPlease enter the job number in the subject line when applying. Applicants considered for interviews will be contacted. www.saskhealthauthority.ca https://saskhealthauthority.libguides.com/home Compensation Rate of Pay: 22.60 - 24.21 Closes: 14 June, 2024 Saskatchewan Health Authority Library Regina , SK Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
